summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, amending Sections 23.46.004, 23.47.004, 23.47.012, 23.47.042, 23.49.011, 23.50.028, 23.53.015, 23.53.030, 23.54.015, 23.71.038, 23.76.004, 23.76.006, and 25.06.110 of the Seattle Municipal Code in order to carry out the Council's intent as stated in all prior ordinances, including Ordinances 120967, 121093, 121115, 121145, 121196, 121277, and 121278, and to correct typographical errors and otherwise accurately reflect the Council's intention.
